file.name: allOf_composition_discriminator_recursive.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: OAI Specification example for Polymorphism
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /status:
    get:
      responses:
        '201':
          description: desc

components:
  schemas:
    TokenMetadata:
      type: object
      properties:
        tag1:
          type: string

    Token:
      type: object
      required:
        - type
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        metadata:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TokenMetadata'
      discriminator:
        propertyName: type
        mapping:
          string: '#/components/schemas/StringToken'
          expression: '#/components/schemas/ExpressionToken'

    StringToken:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token'
        - type: object
          properties:
            value:
              type: string

    ExpressionToken:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token'
        - type: object
          properties:
            tokens:
              type: array
              items:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Token'
